    "rules": [
      "Hero MOVE: Blocked by grid boundaries (0 to gridSize-1) and cells occupied by any enemy.",
      "Hero ATTACK: Targets enemy at Manhattan distance 1. If multiple, targets the one with the lowest ID.",
      "Enemy AI: 1. If Manhattan distance == 1, attack hero. 2. Else, move to minimize distance using tie-breaks. 3. If all distance-minimizing moves blocked, stay put.",
      "Victory: Triggered immediately when all enemy hp <= 0.",
      "Defeat: Triggered immediately when hero hp <= 0.",
      "Finished: Triggered when the Command Sequence is empty and status is still PLAYING.",
      "Turn counter: increment turn by exactly 1 for every hero action applied, INCLUDING the action that triggers VICTORY or DEFEAT (an immediate win on the first action yields turn=1)."
    ],
